name: Salary Calculator
tagline: The salary calculator works out your salary left after deductions.
body:
### Welcome to the Salary Calculator
The aim of the salary calculator is to eventually be able to calculate the left over money for any individual/couple after tax, insurance, rent, mortgage, lease, shopping, gym and other outgoings to help people buying a new home for the first time see what money they might have to play with if they move out.
